Package frogger.util

  • Class Summary
    Class Description
    CollisionChecker
    CollisionChecker is a utility class that checks for Actor collisions involving a Frog at every tick.
    CollisionHandler
    CollisionHandler is a utility class that handles the consequences of collisions between Actors.
    HiscoreReader
    HiscoreReader reads the top 10 entries from a given hiscore file.
    HiscoreWriter
    HiscoreWriter writes entries into a hiscore file.
  • Enum Summary
    Enum Description
    LaneBuilder
    LaneBuilder is a singleton utility class that uses the Prototype, Builder and Factory pattern to instantiate lanes of PanningActors.
    MusicPlayer
    MusicPlayer is a singleton utility enum that handles background music.
    StageManager
    StageManager is a singleton utility class which handles the stages of the app.
